{"tid":1968128,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"★阿媽收起廁紙免被濫用　不孝子大怒揮拳毆母被捕","createTime":"2020-04-11T12:17:18.000Z","updateTime":"2020-04-12T11:52:39.000Z","uid":19454,"like":3,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"cc9d4c096d7bc7934428ec2e7fd2faf77218dd22","tid":1968128,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-11T12:17:18.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/dw/20200411/325678395633569792.jpeg/w-b9ZEHMK7cNaGiZWvSIKeZT3HqKdp3VgPj_4YD4_-E?v=w1280r16_9\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2Fdw%2F20200411%2F325678395633569792.jpeg%2Fw-b9ZEHMK7cNaGiZWvSIKeZT3HqKdp3VgPj_4YD4_-E%3Fv%3Dw1280r16_9&h=ee702893&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n美國加州一名男子改不掉濫用廁紙的壞習慣，其母只好將廁紙直接收起，沒料引起他不滿，更一度怒極揮拳毆打母親，最終被當地警方帶走調查。<br />\n<br />\n洛杉磯警方表示，周一（6日）凌晨3時接報，居於當地北部的26歲男子Adrian Yan於寓所與母親因廁紙用量起爭執，期間疑曾揮拳毆打母親，警員遂當場拘捕他。<br />\n<br />\n警員向Adrian的媽媽查問時，她表示自疫情爆發以來，當地的廁紙供應持續緊張，然而兒子卻改不掉濫用廁紙的壞習慣，只好收起廁紙一了百了，沒料引來兒子不滿，雙方遂起口角，後來更發生暴力事件。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.hk01.com/%E7%86%B1%E7%88%86%E8%A9%B1%E9%A1%8C/459820/%E6%96%B0%E5%86%A0%E8%82%BA%E7%82%8E-%E9%98%BF%E5%AA%BD%E6%94%B6%E8%B5%B7%E5%BB%81%E7%B4%99%E5%85%8D%E8%A2%AB%E6%BF%AB%E7%94%A8-%E7%BE%8E%E5%9C%8B%E4%B8%8D%E5%AD%9D%E5%AD%90%E5%A4%A7%E6%80%92%E6%8F%AE%E6%8B%B3%E6%AF%86%E6%AF%8D%E8%A2%AB%E6%8D%95\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hk01.com%2F%25E7%2586%25B1%25E7%2588%2586%25E8%25A9%25B1%25E9%25A1%258C%2F459820%2F%25E6%2596%25B0%25E5%2586%25A0%25E8%2582%25BA%25E7%2582%258E-%25E9%2598%25BF%25E5%25AA%25BD%25E6%2594%25B6%25E8%25B5%25B7%25E5%25BB%2581%25E7%25B4%2599%25E5%2585%258D%25E8%25A2%25AB%25E6%25BF%25AB%25E7%2594%25A8-%25E7%25BE%258E%25E5%259C%258B%25E4%25B8%258D%25E5%25AD%259D%25E5%25AD%2590%25E5%25A4%25A7%25E6%2580%2592%25E6%258F%25AE%25E6%258B%25B3%25E6%25AF%2586%25E6%25AF%258D%25E8%25A2%25AB%25E6%258D%2595&d=pQk%2FYDfxyk1It%2BdH9Wj1W822uFAamDTqma2v4g3iiws%3D&h=c7b6d5c3\" data-auto-link 